<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618148>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pronotum and scutellum of the genus Eupyrochroa, dorsal view. A, D: E. insignita; B, C, E, F: E. limbaticollis; A–C: male; D–F: female. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10618148/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618154>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Adult of Eupyrochroa insignita. A. habitus, male, dorsal view; B–C. head, dorsal view: B. male; C. female; D–E. antenna, left: D. male; E. female; F–G. tegmen: F. dorsal view; G. lateral view; H–I. penis: H. dorsal view; I. lateral view. Scale bars: 5 mm (A), 1 mm (others)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10618154/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618156>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Larva of Eupyrochroa insignita. A. habitus, dorsal view; B–C. head and pronotum: B. dorsal view; C. ventral view; D. urogomphal plate and urogomphi, posterior view. Scale bars: 5 mm (A), 1 mm (others)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10618156/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618158>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Larva of Eupyrochroa insignita. A. urogomphal plate and urogomphi, dorsal view; B. sternites VIII–X, urogomphal plate, and urogomphi, ventral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10618158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

